<h1>Ian Cobane Traditional Green Oak and Timber Frame Building, Design Construction South East UK</h1>

We are a south east uk based company, proud to offer you years of experienced craftsmanship in the production of Traditional green Oak Frame Building and timber frame building, for both domestic and commercial environments. We design and build in a very wide range of Traditional green oak frame building styles. We specialise in the design and manufacture of green oak framed buildings and the creation of fine pieces of furniture. Traditional skills are used to construct houses, office spaces, sun-rooms, garages, extensions, summer houses etc. Whatever you want; we can create in exquisite traditional green oak frame building form. Our skills are used to produce traditional timber frame building styles to marry with existing features, to produce an eclectic mix of traditional and contemporary or to create a totally modern image. We apply our full design service to all our timber frame building constructions, whether it\'s producing extra living space or interior or exterior wood work. Our carpentry skills can be applied to the production of bespoke traditional green oak frame building, doors, handrails, staircases, furniture and kitchens using the same solid wood traditions we apply to our buildings. We will produce pieces sympathetically, to your requirements, using time honoured traditions combined with 21st Century technology. © Cobane Traditional timber Frame Building, Design Construction south east UK

